snippet.title: Epic Dumpster Bear Trailer
snippet.description: Epic Dumpster Bear is an action packed platforming game inspired by the 16-bit classics.  Over 70 levels filled with tricky platforming, challenging bosses, and secret exits to be discovered.  Coming Spring 2016 to the Wii U eShop
